data.title: Okay. It’s been about a month since I first saw The Sandman on Netflix. I have since watched it again with Eric and started it yet another...
data.meta_description:
92 likes, 14 comments - tkoakley7 on October 12, 2022: "Okay. It’s been about a month since I first saw The Sandman on Netflix. I have since watched it again with Eric and started it yet another time this week. 

I can admit that I’m more than just a fanatic at this point, I have since had different dreams, and have made more connections than ever between my dream state and my waking life, something I used to connect to but had since lost enthusiasm for.

Has anyone else watched it and had their dream state completely changed? Or even just been as enthralled in the story as myself?".
